 
<p>
  Thugs perceive black teenagers, and even children, <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2022/jul/05/they-saw-me-as-calculating-not-a-child-how-adultification-leads-to-black-children-being-treated-as-criminals">as more adult than whites of the same age</a> &mdash; and treat them as culpable.

 